        <abstract>
            <para>Records generated by Sheffield and Rotherham Wildlife Trust staff and volunteers, and public records submitted to SRWT. Geographic range predominantly across Sheffield and Rotherham area. Dataset includes: Public casual records, SRWT casual records, SRWT monitoring and surveying records.
Data stored within the BRC iRecord data warehouse.</para>
